            "title": "英股全日升1點　德法股市再度回軟",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲股市偏軟，受關稅困擾汽車股受壓。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市回吐0.15%，報540點，早段一度反彈0.62%；汽車股下挫1.7%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230711-094811_20191002_EUSTOCK_-source-ap_-1-1-2.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230711-094811_20191002_EUSTOCK_-source-ap_-1-1-2.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數表現反覆，早段最多升約0.5%，其後一度回落，收市報8542點，升1點，連升兩日。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德法股市再度回軟，德國DAX指數收報22567點，跌109點，跌幅約0.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數於8000點水平得而復失，收報7938點，跌50點，跌幅逾0.6%，創逾5星期新低。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報37999點，走低0.8%或307點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報12821點，上揚0.14%或17點。</p>\n</div>",
